name: Digit Draw
description: Predict handwritten digits in the browser using a tensorflow CNN trained on the MNIST handwritten digits dataset.

name: Doodle Draw
description: Draw a doodle in the browser and get predictions in real-time using a TensorFlow.js model trained on the Google Quick, Draw! dataset.

name: Snake AI (DQN)
description: Deep Q-Network trained to play Snake in Python with TensorFlow/Keras. Model exported to TensorFlow.js for an in browser live demo.
